data.title: Windows Server 2003 R2 x86 Edition
data.meta_description: Windows Server 2003 R2 is the next scheduled release of the Windows Server System, Ahead of Windows Longhorn Server. 'R2' stands for 'Release 2'. It includes The Base Windows Server 2003 Install, plus SP1, all Feature Packs to date, and any hotfixes released since SP1. Windows Server 2003 R2...
